   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": "# VNA 控制"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": "**scikit-rf** 有几个虚拟仪器类，位于 `skrf.vi` 模块中。本页面演示了对 PNA 的基本控制"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": "## 连接和查询仪器 ID"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "    from skrf.vi.vna import keysight\n",
    "\n",
    "    instr = keysight.PNA(\"TCPIP0::192.168.0.2::INSTR\")\n",
    "    instr.id"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": "## 作为 scikit-rf Network 检索 S 参数"
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "    ntwk =  instr.get_snp_network()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": []
  }
